data.text:
Description

This brochure is in Dari.

Autopsy A5 information brochure for health professionals to provide to parents who speak Dari. These brochures encourages parents to think about what’s important to them following a stillbirth, and support families to ask questions of their healthcare team and write down the things of importance.

Brochures are provided free of charge. The maximum number of brochures per order is 10.

Please note that these resources are only suitable for clinical health services. We are unable to provide these resources to non-health services.

Shipping

Brochure orders are dispatched every Tuesday and may take about 14 days to reach you. Please ensure that you provide an address where someone is available to receive the order from our trusted delivery drivers.
